In a bid to showcase its services, Cloud Hotel and Suites at Diamond Plaza, Parklands hosted a lavish dinner on Tuesday evening for a select group of invitees. The hotel, a sister company to Concord Hotel plans to make the dinner a regular event in order to allow patrons and management to network and exchange feedback. In attendance were Jumia Travels EA head of revenue management Yared Kifle and Chatur Group chief financial officer Suresh Bachheta.